---
import "@/styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "@/components/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  SEOTitle="Sovereign AI | PrincipalAI"
  SEODescription="Private and controlled AI deployment for organisations that need data sovereignty, security, and governance."
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#071f3f] via-[#123f86] to-[#e8f4ff] px-8 py-24 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-blue-100">
        Sovereign AI
      </p>
      <h1 class="max-w-5xl font-serif text-5xl font-bold leading-tight sm:text-6xl">
        AI under your control.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
        PrincipalAI helps organisations deploy AI systems in private, controlled environments while retaining control over data, infrastructure, models, and sensitive workflows.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
        Request a demonstration
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main>
    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            The problem
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Public AI tools are not enough for high-trust organisations.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Many organisations want to use AI but cannot expose sensitive information, intellectual property, client material, operational data, or confidential analysis to external systems.
          </p>
          <p>
            Sovereign AI provides a way to use modern AI capability while maintaining stronger control over where information is stored, how models are accessed, and how outputs are governed.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
          What it supports
        </p>
        <h2 class="max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
          AI deployment designed around privacy, control, and governance.
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Private deployment</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Deploy AI systems in approved environments, including private cloud, dedicated servers, or on-premise infrastructure.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Data control</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Keep sensitive documents, data, prompts, and outputs within controlled organisational boundaries.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Access governance</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Support user roles, permissions, review points, and governance over AI-enabled workflows.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-md bg-white p-7 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Operational assurance</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700">
              Improve confidence through controlled deployment, traceable workflows, and clear separation from public AI tools.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Example applications
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Built for organisations that need AI without losing control.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Private research assistants connected to organisational knowledge sources.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Secure policy, regulatory, and technical advisory workflows.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            AI systems for sensitive infrastructure, health, energy, and public-sector analysis.
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-5">
            Controlled AI deployment for teams that need governance, auditability, and assurance.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-50 px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">
            Why PrincipalAI
          </p>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-900">
            Sovereign AI connected to real analytical work.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
          <p>
            PrincipalAI designs AI systems for organisations that need more than a public chatbot. Our approach connects private AI deployment with evidence retrieval, modelling, reporting, workflow automation, and decision support.
          </p>
          <p>
            We focus on practical systems that preserve organisational control while improving productivity, insight, and analytical consistency.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#071f3f] px-8 py-20 text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl font-serif text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Deploy AI securely, privately, and on your terms.
        </h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-blue-50">
          Talk to PrincipalAI about private AI deployment, data sovereignty, governance, and controlled AI operations.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-md bg-blue-600 px-7 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
          Request a demonstration
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
